  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WAF
  MaxHealth: 50
  Strength: 10
  EntityName: Web Application Firewall
  Description: '<color=#FF4444>50 HP</color> | <color=#FFAA00>10 ATK</color> | <color=#00CCFF>55
    EN</color>

    Protects web applications by analyzing HTTP traffic at the application
    level and blocking specific attacks, such as SQL injection or cross-site scripting
    (XSS). Unlike a standard firewall, it thoroughly examines the content of requests
    and acts as a filtering shield between the internet and the web server.

    Can
    attack up to 5 players at a time.

    <color=#BF00FF>Enemies: Ransomware, Trojan,
    DDOS, Zero Day Exploit, Supply Chain Attack.</color>'
